Melinda McGraw https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Melinda_McGraw 0 Melinda McGraw is an American actress. She has starred in movies such as Albino Alligator (1996), Wrongfully Accused (1998), and Nutty Professor II: The Klumps (2000), and is also known for her television performances on The Commish, The X-Files, NCIS and Mad Men.
